**File**: `frontend/src/hooks/useDeepgramSTT.ts` (lines 70-74)

**Problem**: The audio conversion doesn't validate audio data:

```typescript
const int16 = new Int16Array(float32.length);
for (let i = 0; i < float32.length; i++) {
  const s = Math.max(-1, Math.min(1, float32[i]));  // ← No NaN/Infinity check
